flowchart LR
  subgraph Orient
    direction TB
    O1[User views organizational cockpit] --> O2[User inspects freshness and access caveats]
  end
  subgraph Investigate
    direction TB
    I1[User asks why launch is at risk] --> I2[User follows citations into graph and timeline]
    I2 --> I3[User reviews uncertainty or abstention]
  end
  subgraph Simulate
    direction TB
    S1[User confirms assumptions and interventions] --> S2[User compares baseline with scenario]
    S2 --> S3[User inspects sensitivity and missing data]
  end
  subgraph Act
    direction TB
    A1[User previews exact Jira change and rollback] --> A2[Two distinct approvers bind the exact payload]
    A2 --> A3[User verifies receipt audit and graph update]
  end
  O2 --> I1
  I3 --> S1
  S3 --> A1
